GROUP : A5

Programming – C Language Assignments

This repository contains a set of assignments developed for the Programming course, implemented in the C programming language.

The projects focus on practicing fundamental programming concepts such as:

basic syntax and structure of C
memory management and arrays
functions and modular program design
input/output handling
working with simple algorithms and data processing

Each assignment represents a separate exercise aimed at improving practical programming skills and understanding core concepts of the C language through hands-on implementation.
